; Dummy_LVL2 strips: Idle 66x35 (2 frames), Move 396x35 (12 frames), Dash 132x35 (4 frames)
; All frames → 33x35 per cell.
; Stats sit between LVL1 (HP=21, spd=55, dmg=5) and LVL3 (HP=24, spd=60, dmg=6),
; but LVL2 is a little sturdier because it now softly screens nearby ranged allies.
; No palette-unify shader — LVL2 enters mid-wave-3 after the tutorial palette is established.

